title: Iron Maiden - The Beast Is Rising [320k MP3]
description:
Iron Maiden - The Beast Is Rising is a 4 disc compilation by the British heavy metal band Iron Maiden, released on 14 November 2014. Released digitally, exclusively on The Pirate Bay, it is the first release of smb Music Entertainment's The 'Rising' series. 62 tracks over four discs, almost four hours of classic Iron Maiden. Tracks taken from The Soundhouse Tapes thru The Final Frontier and every album in between. As of 2014 the most comprehensive Iron Maiden collection available.
